Patch Set 2:

@Kairat it does seem like https://github.com/openstack/glance/blob/48ee8ef4793ed40397613193f09872f474c11abe/glance/api/middleware/context.py#L195 should be referring to the context_is_admin policy rule rather than to this conf setting, for consistency. We shouldn't need both context_is_admin and the conf setting you referred to.

We could do something about that here, but I'd just as soon split that out into a separate patch. It's something that should be fixed with or without this patch.
